<div class="email-container">
  <div class="email-card">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1 class="email-title">邮箱验证</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-body">
      <p class="email-text">你好，</p>
      
      <p class="email-text">请确认 <strong><%= @user.email %></strong> 是你要在账户中使用的邮箱地址。如果你忘记密码，我们将向该邮箱发送重置链接。</p>
      
      <div class="email-alert">
        <p class="email-alert-text">你必须点击下方链接以确认收到此邮件。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="email-button-container">
        <%= link_to "确认，使用此邮箱", identity_email_verification_url(sid: @signed_id), class: "email-button" %>
      </div>
      
      <p class="email-text" style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 16px;">或复制以下链接到浏览器：</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #0066cc; word-break: break-all; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 8px; border-radius: 4px;"><%= identity_email_verification_url(sid: @signed_id) %></p>
      
      <hr class="email-divider">
      
      <p class="email-footer">有问题或需要帮助？直接回复此邮件，我们的客服团队会协助你解决。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
